    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平访华前欧洲对中国发起医疗器械调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/eu-opens-investigation-into-china-s-medical-device-procurement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟对中国采购医疗设备发起调查，这是习近平主席五年来首次访问欧盟之前一系列加剧紧张局势的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/eu-opens-investigation-into-china-s-medical-device-procurement</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 01:00:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着经济挑战的加剧，马克龙瞄准法国的繁文缛节</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/macron-targets-french-bureaucracy-as-economic-challenges-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃马纽埃尔·马克龙(Emmanuel Macron)的目标是削减阻碍法国企业发展的官僚机构，因为他的总统任期面临着日益严重的经济逆风。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/macron-targets-french-bureaucracy-as-economic-challenges-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 19:11:40 GMT</pubDate>
